OL,5,Cfire fined #90k
OL,7,FA husband and wife landlord team who
OL,8,Frented out a "grossly overcrowded"
OL,9,Feast London flat where an e-bike fire
OL,10,Fled to the death of a tenant have been
OL,11,Ffined more than #90,000.
OL,13,FFather-of-two Mizanur Rahman, 41, died
OL,14,Ffrom the effects of smoke inhalation
OL,15,Fafter the fire in the early hours of
OL,16,FMarch 5 2023 at Maddocks House in
OL,17,FShadwell.
