OL,4,Covercrowded' flat before fatal e-bike
OL,5,Cfire fined #90k
OL,7,FParents-of-six Sofina Begum, 52, and
OL,8,FAminur Rahman, 55, had previously
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to a total of nine
OL,10,Fhousing offences.
OL,12,FJudge Emma Smith, sitting at
OL,13,FSnaresbrook Crown Court, previously
OL,14,Fsaid she was looking at sentencing the
OL,15,Fcouple, of Wapping, east London, not
OL,16,Fon the fatality or the fire, but on
OL,17,Fthe housing offences which they
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to in November 2023.
