OL,5,Cfire fined #90k
OL,7,FOn Thursday, Judge Smith ordered Begum
OL,8,Fto pay a fine of #10,000 and #2,000 in
OL,9,Fprosecution costs. She was also told
OL,10,Fto pay a confiscation order of #78,049.
OL,12,FRahman, who was said to be of "no
OL,13,Fmeans", was ordered to pay a fine of
OL,14,F#2,000 and a confiscation order of
OL,15,F#1.1p.
OL,17,FThe court heard the pair had no source
OL,18,Fof income other than the value of the
OL,19,FMaddocks House property which stood at
OL,20,F#155,000.
