OL,5,Cfire fined #90k
OL,7,FSentencing, Judge Smith said: "I am
OL,8,Fsatisfied the two of you were equally
OL,9,Finvolved in the criminality and shared
OL,10,Ffinancial gain... You showed a blatant
OL,11,Fdisregard for the law and the
OL,12,Foccupants."
OL,14,FThe property, which was licenced for
OL,15,Fthree people from two households, is
OL,16,Fbelieved to have been occupied by 23
OL,17,Fpeople.
