OL,5,Cfire fined #90k
OL,7,FTenants were told not to use the flat
OL,8,Fas a postal address as it could get
OL,9,Fthe couple in trouble, the court heard.
OL,11,FFormer residents of the flat have said
OL,12,Fthey paid about #90 a week, where some
OL,13,Fshared beds or slept on the floor of
OL,14,Fthe two-bedroom ex-council flat. There
OL,15,Fwere 18 beds, including bunk beds, at
OL,16,Fthe property.
OL,18,FThe blaze was started accidentally by
OL,19,Fa faulty lithium ion e-bike battery
OL,20,Fthat was charging at the time, the
OL,21,FLondon Fire Brigade have said.
