OL,7,FInvestigations are still ongoing and a
OL,8,Fcivil matter has already been lodged.
OL,10,FBegum, whose name was on the licence,
OL,11,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to six
OL,12,Foffences including knowingly
OL,13,Fpermitting unlicensed occupation, four
OL,14,Fcounts of failing to comply with
OL,15,Flicence conditions and failing to
OL,16,Fcomply with the requirements of a
OL,17,Flicence notice.
