OL,3,CCouple who rented 'grossly
OL,4,Covercrowded' flat before fatal e-bike
OL,5,Cfire fined #90k
OL,7,FBut one of the residents told liaison
OL,8,Fofficers that he paid rent to Rahman.
OL,10,FThe judge noted that a month after the
OL,11,Ffire, Begum made an application for an
OL,12,Fextension of the lost space which did
OL,13,Fnot mention the fire or that the
OL,14,Fproperty was uninhabitable, and said
OL,15,Fshe was living at the flat and it was
OL,16,Fovercrowded.
OL,18,FThe judge also noted that this event
OL,19,Ftook place after the charges she was
OL,20,Fdealing with.
