OL,7,FThe Executive Mayor of Tower Hamlets,
OL,8,FLutfur Rahman, said: "It is completely
OL,9,Funacceptable that some landlords
OL,10,Fcontinue to exploit tenants by
OL,11,Fallowing overcrowding, flouting
OL,12,Fessential safety regulations, and
OL,13,Fputting people's lives at risk.
OL,15,F"Our thoughts and prayers remain with
OL,16,Fthe family and friends of Mizanur
OL,17,FRahman, who tragically lost his life
OL,18,Fin the fire, caused by a faulty e-bike
OL,19,Fbattery, at Maddocks House, and with
OL,20,Fall those affected by this devastating
OL,21,Fincident.
