OL,7,F"We are clamping down on rogue
OL,8,Flandlords who operate in our borough.
OL,9,FWe pursued this prosecution and the
OL,10,Fcourt's decision sends a clear
OL,11,Fmessage: we will not tolerate criminal
OL,12,Flandlords who endanger lives for
OL,13,Fprofit. We will continue to do
OL,14,Feverything we can to ensure such cases
OL,15,Fare brought to justice in order to
OL,16,Fprotect our community and we urge all
OL,17,Flocal authorities to do the same.
